# read_csv Exceptions not related to filesystem


pd.errors.EmptyDataError — the file is completely empty (zero bytes).
pd.errors.ParserError — the file content can't be parsed as CSV (malformed rows,
inconsistent number of columns, bad delimiters).
UnicodeDecodeError — the file uses an encoding that doesn't match the defaulti
(UTF-8)
